  "title": "<div>Left behind a summer </div>",
  "content": "<div>Left behind a summer </div>\n<div>cubic mint, </div>\n<div>sat sill</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>(ignored). </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>The charm collected dust,</div>\n<div>not your ghost;</div>\n<div>by Fall,</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>swallowed. </div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Snow blush on my pill—oh,</div>\n<div>this again!</div>\n<div>Amen,</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>my son.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>A boy; can't help but ask:</div>\n<div>you’ll be back</div>\n<div>two-more</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>at least?</div>",
